{"tid":1107564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劏舖變死場】曾瘋搶慧星匯今陷無人之境 商戶轟大業主：完全無配套｜","createTime":"2019-04-15T10:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T02:31:04.000Z","uid":20738,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"62dd3af4312b4e3f7482f2b4620d969f693eff29","tid":1107564,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664060_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_term=utm-generator&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664060_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_term%3Dutm-generator%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUat%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=19602f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_664060_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_term%3Dutm-generator%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=444605af\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_664060_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_term=utm-generator&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劏場十室九空，慘變死場。將軍澳「慧安商場」內的巨型舖位，2016年被資深投資者蔡志忠等人以8800萬購入，即分拆成88間小型商鋪出售，全部售出後可套現2億元。惟現時卻爆發欠管理費風波，代理解釋跟大業主收不齊管理費，以至未能上繳有關。本刊致電「POPSTAR 慧星匯」的小業主作了解，竟道出另一版本。大業主在交鋪時，跟預期有很大落差。原本開心收舖，怎料卻由小業主變苦主。<br />\n<br />\n有買家表示，原本打算買舖位經營食肆，不過收舖時跟當初想像有很大落差。想經營食肆，卻沒有來去水、也沒有三相電。<br />\n<br />\n翻查報道，「POPSTAR 慧星匯」這個巨型舖位佔地約二萬呎，及後分拆成88個舖位發售。當日首批50個單位，入場價大約200萬元，還限制一客只能入三票，可想而知炒風有多熾熱。當時請來歌手吳國敬及藝人麥長青負責攪珠，場面熱鬧。有小業主直言，當初被代理遊說購入，但起初預計的四至五厘回報落空，商場沒有人流，最近更被商場管理公司追收管理費，矛頭直指劏場小業主沒準時交管理費所致。<br />\n<br />\n小業主向本刊反映，原本大業主承諾在商場外放置大型屏幕，但入伙至今仍未兌現。根據代理行傳來的資料顯示，「POPSTAR 慧星匯」88個劏鋪中，暫時已成功租出30間，但現場所見，真正營業卻是寥寥無幾。<br />\n<br />\n亦有小業主反映，商場完全沒人管理，卻只懂收錢，地也沒有人掃，垃圾箱也沒有一個，情況已維持多月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【劏舖變死場】揭將軍澳慧星匯拖欠管理費 業權分散小業主難自救   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QajwHfV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQajwHfV.png&h=656313d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3412656371f5231c011484b05b781cceec9ae","tid":1107564,"uid":7369,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩先會買嚟放租"},{"pid":"447fb674a82283bc6cc92959e8177c66838feace","tid":1107564,"uid":40682,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"無人之境係咁用㗎咩 依家啲記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c22f8486bbd5128abe8d1a5d1235a341bcff56","tid":1107564,"uid":37524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"慰安商場"},{"pid":"0cc6cc6982476a54801b64a1fee2c44dc1c4353e","tid":1107564,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"買領展房產基金咪算lo"},{"pid":"a73cba3d03b923021ed4393bd1683ab3c307b513","tid":1107564,"uid":12542,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實十個劏場十個結局都係咁<br />\n點解仲有人中伏"},{"pid":"4623041269cc2d81fe5cf1691dd67b859f41d962","tid":1107564,"uid":55924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傻鳩發現案 <br />\n唔睇新聞？</span>"},{"pid":"3d5bbe27a0f6db4ce329eccb4daf2cdb784fe708","tid":1107564,"uid":202340,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"a73cba3d03b923021ed4393bd1683ab3c307b513","tid":1107564,"uid":12542,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實十個劏場十個結局都係咁<br />\n點解仲有人中伏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"深之都撐到依家先有少少改善"},{"pid":"d28721f8be5d556df38db5f35486a24071931c23","tid":1107564,"uid":40682,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2