5e05a0b3d3676c3a7602a34","tid":1107564,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a73cba3d03b923021ed4393bd1683ab3c307b513","tid":1107564,"uid":12542,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實十個劏場十個結局都係咁<br />\n點解仲有人中伏"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"好似得葵涌廣場一個旺場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"葵廣一個鋪大好多<br />\n而且d鋪係賣晒出去唔係大業主擁有<br />\n所以個商場係無權控制邊d鋪應該開係邊同有無得留低，同香港其他大商場大業主話晒事好唔同<br />\n基本上葵廣d鋪係可以亂開<br />\n先造就葵廣而家個旺場（同混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"葵廣應該都唔會再有第二個，甚至可以話係嗰個時代先至可以做到嘅場，根本無法複製。"},{"pid":"8eb0f9ac611242ac53b1f874635ac265cc9afaec","tid":1107564,"uid":8461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"熟少少將軍澳嘅都知慧安園咩環境啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身2樓就已經係啲做熟客類生意<br />\n補習美容飛髮紋身中醫貨倉<br />\n<br />\n食嘢就得幾間<br />\n無咩必要都唔會上去，因為無嘢for你行<br />\n而家最入間酒樓都執鳩埋仲要變劏場<br />\n<br />\n鬼影都無隻已經係十幾年嘅事<br />\n做生意？咪攪笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6514d504070fa9ef5ae4aa308b0a061ebdba3df4","tid":1107564,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc3412656371f5231c011484b05b781cceec9ae","tid":1107564,"uid":7369,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩先會買嚟放租"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"一舖養三代嘅只有喺地舖先至會出現，商舖唔係"},{"pid":"a62961bba3b9a28772881f261ee4774abb6e9cee","tid":1107564,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4491e21b793dbcc4fd68bc053c84b2ba5a83f1","tid":1107564,"uid":248116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a553ad157e61d485c19baab2076e126d8bba6dd4","tid":1107564,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a73cba3d03b923021ed4393bd1683ab