,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"所以劏鋪大王可以玩咁多次，同類招數已經試過好多次。"},{"pid":"3f0062c8e82a0398826f80710dd83b744c2dbaf1","tid":1107564,"uid":78770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8eb0f9ac611242ac53b1f874635ac265cc9afaec","tid":1107564,"uid":8461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"熟少少將軍澳嘅都知慧安園咩環境啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身2樓就已經係啲做熟客類生意<br />\n補習美容飛髮紋身中醫貨倉<br />\n<br />\n食嘢就得幾間<br />\n無咩必要都唔會上去，因為無嘢for你行<br />\n而家最入間酒樓都執鳩埋仲要變劏場<br />\n<br />\n鬼影都無隻已經係十幾年嘅事<br />\n做生意？咪攪笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"早十年都仲好少少 起碼有間酒樓係到<br />\n依家慧安都係得剪頭髮 小食 速遞 補習做到落去 <br />\n仲係講緊下面嗰層 上面一層真係好撚靜<br />\n佢慧星匯哩個位 係正以前酒樓個位 又遠又唔近電梯<br />\n今日岩岩先去完嗰到整啲野 劏又劏得細 鋪位又難搵 十間有八間都係吉<br />\n淨返兩間都係拍下烏蠅"},{"pid":"a351729575a88f1c1f65e7f6effe61931523b585","tid":1107564,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6514d504070fa9ef5ae4aa308b0a061ebdba3df4","tid":1107564,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc3412656371f5231c011484b05b781cceec9ae","tid":1107564,"uid":7369,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"戇鳩先會買嚟放租"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"一舖養三代嘅只有喺地舖先至會出現，商舖唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"果個位真硬蕉, 又唔迎地鐵又冇巴士站!"},{"pid":"68428514fff7bfc9aa27dae014c16502e33aa192","tid":1107564,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b022f1fa4f689b876534777135e0029ccef67","tid":1107564,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee71cd4f86143c691fccdf694aac69c34e6232d9","tid":1107564,"uid":39710,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"有邊個場咁劏完係成功？<br />\n<br />\n你睇下旺角東京銀座(而家叫砵蘭180+)、尖嘴首都商場 、尖嘴其士大廈地庫(尖東堡)、深水埗深之都<br />\n<br />\n全部啲出租率低到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"而家發達鳥搬走左<br />\n深之都係咪又變返死場"},{"pid":"250fc6d8c0a58235fa611d22ca19238b995f3fa7","tid":1107564,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"之前睇過啲報道，有啲退休人士諗住買鋪退休後嘆世界<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果就係「退休?下一世啦」"},{"pid":"04fff1a3025c11692ecb7dd0f0a1c297a3a7c301","tid":1107564,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"屌你又有麥包份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怪之得啦"},{"pid":"b86e9988c2895989707a2b4751091f33cb8ac98e","tid":1107564,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"劏場入面鋪位同本身慧安園出面細鋪位size差唔多, 所以叫比想象中好, 不過行人通道就窄到死。<br />\n買黎投資就真係等收皮啦, 洗米華d野都好信既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b6920c5b852460fbd57b671f380eaa638e040b","tid":1107564,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78974ac1727973c7f4b4a5549d6a08a6ffa84af9","tid":1107564,"uid":20738,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"3d5bbe27a0f6db4ce329eccb4daf2cdb784fe708","tid":1107564,"uid":202340,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"a73cba3d03b923021ed4393bd1683ab3c307b513","tid":1107564,"uid":12542,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實十個劏場十個結局都係咁<br />\n點解仲有人中伏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"深之都撐到依家先有少少改善"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"諗起以前舊燈有人鍾意探險去搵嗰啲死寂商場<br />\n<br />\n一講到死寂商場，個個就一定會講到「觀塘碼頭廣場」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"依家旺到仆街"},{"pid":"9ae8a8aa0ba71f33c0c707430b16ccd53d28db24","tid":1107564,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b6920c5b852460fbd57b671f380eaa638e040b","tid":1107564,"uid":18587