score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"每一排都有劏場賣鋪，賣晒廣告吹到放租好好賺水人落搭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba6d7cdf534afb1b07ce766595ddabe0e50984b","tid":1107564,"uid":54654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e39c65e54aa2a0c0582accfce725b2628d2a7131","tid":1107564,"uid":27485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb809e668f387f28cc5955692be0c5e0764c5073","tid":1107564,"uid":54654,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"慧安商場本身都係好靜，得啲美容、小食店、餐廳、補習社之類，做下街坊生意咁樣。二樓個劏場位置上手好似係酒樓嚟。<br />\n<br />\n邊有人會專登入去行吖，一定死。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"細個成日去抄save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔離又有啲鋪比人玩卡<br />\n係一個幾歡樂既商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"我唔係區內人，不過慧安商場嗰間餃子幾平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf0981ee07d93ad02c5ada45edfa1c000c25e7","tid":1107564,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"見到劏場加麥包都知瀨嘢率達99.9% 啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}